@startuml
title Fetching Conversation History
actor User
participant Client
participant Server
participant FileManager

User -> Client : scroll up / request older messages
Client -> Server : requestOlderMessages(conversationID, oldestMessageID)
Server -> FileManager : fetchOlderMessages(conversationID, oldestMessageID)
FileManager --> Server : List<Message>
Server --> Client : List<Message>
Client --> User : display older messages
@enduml